  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Even though zksync support EIP-1271 signatures, those signatures are not deterministic.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\nI have a 2 out of 3 Multisig and create a signerkey derrived from my contract-signature, which contains signatures of the first 2 keys. I may loose the second key and generate a valid contract-signature from key1 and key 3. Both signatures are valid, but not the same, which means in both cases different signer-keys would be generated.",
